<%- include('partials/head', { title: pageTitle }) %>
<body>
  <div class="page-container simple-page about-page">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
      <section class="about-section">
        <div class="about-top">
          <div class="about-hand">
            <img src="/images/about/pointing-hand.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
          </div>
          <div class="about-intro">
            <p>
              <strong>RIGHT NOW</strong> I’m pursuing an MSW. My professional experience is long and varied.
              My near-future intent is to practice analytically oriented psychotherapy. My current and long held
              practice has to do with reading and writing, and I think that’s the practice that will most define
              my career, in due time. This site won’t exist for long. Thank you for visiting.
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>YOU CAN</strong> leave me a note <a href="mailto:adriennecaffarel1@gmail.com">here</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-middle">
          <div class="about-tools-block">
            <h3><strong>HERE ARE</strong> some competencies and things I think about:</h3>
            <ul class="about-tools">
              <li>Corporate Operations and Infrastructure</li>
              <li>Self Hosting</li>
              <li>History of the world since the reconquest of the Iberian Peninsula</li>
              <li>The impacts of the Marshall Plan</li>
              <li>Cybersecurity</li>
              <li>Desire</li>
              <li>The relationship between modern psychiatry and capital</li>
              <li>History of the Arab Spring</li>
              <li>Religion and Object Relations</li>
              <li>Object Relations and Chronic Illness</li>
              <li>Chronic Illness and Gender</li>
              <li>Gender and Religion</li>
              <li>The Politics of Diagnosis</li>
              <li>Signs and Interpretation</li>
              <li>Race, Class, and Healthcare</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="about-education-block">
            <h3><strong>THIS IS</strong> my education:</h3>
            <div class="about-education">
              <p><strong>University of San Francisco</strong> | BA, Politics | 2016–2020</p>
              <p class="about-fordham-line">
                <span class="about-loading-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span><strong>Fordham University</strong> | MSW | 2026–2028</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="about-spotify" aria-live="polite">
          <p class="about-spotify__title"><strong>THIS IS</strong> what I’m playing on Spotify right now:</p>
          <div class="about-spotify-current" data-spotify-card>
            <p class="about-spotify-current__status" data-spotify-status>Loading Spotify…</p>
            <p class="about-spotify-current__track">
              <span data-spotify-track></span>
              <span class="about-spotify-current__divider" data-spotify-divider aria-hidden="true">/</span>
              <span data-spotify-artist></span>
            </p>
            <a class="about-spotify-current__link" data-spotify-link href="" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Open in Spotify</a>
          </div>
          <div class="spotify-embed" data-spotify-embed></div>
        </section>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="dev-snake-ribbon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="dev-snake-svg" viewBox="0 0 1600 120" preserveAspectRatio="none" role="presentation">
        <defs>
          <path id="dev-snake-path" d="M -320 60 Q -280 20 -240 60 Q -200 100 -160 60 Q -120 20 -80 60 Q -40 100 0 60 Q 40 20 80 60 Q 120 100 160 60 Q 200 20 240 60 Q 280 100 320 60 Q 360 20 400 60 Q 440 100 480 60 Q 520 20 560 60 Q 600 100 640 60 Q 680 20 720 60 Q 760 100 800 60 Q 840 20 880 60 Q 920 100 960 60 Q 1000 20 1040 60 Q 1080 100 1120 60 Q 1160 20 1200 60 Q 1240 100 1280 60 Q 1320 20 1360 60 Q 1400 100 1440 60 Q 1480 20 1520 60 Q 1560 100 1600 60 Q 1640 20 1680 60 Q 1720 100 1760 60 Q 1800 20 1840 60 Q 1880 100 1920 60"></path>
        </defs>
        <text class="dev-snake-text">
          <textPath class="dev-snake-text-path" href="#dev-snake-path" startOffset="0" xml:space="preserve"></textPath>
        </text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/animations.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/building.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
